reviewText: The PowerPoint presentation was disappointing.  Many of my graduate students are interested in creating a consulting business and working via the Internet.  I had hoped to use this in one of my college courses, but the content and interest level were below my expectations.

If you want to discover the internet marketing secrets to launch your coaching practice over the top and keep it there, you can't miss this DVD! Carol Solomon, Master Coach, gives clearcut, easy to implement "You can do it!" strategies that will answer all your questions about domaine names, newsletters, and websites.  New coaches as well as experienced ones will love the cutting edge tech tips that de-mystify the ways to direct potential clients to your website and keep them returning. This DVD is worth it's weight in gold, no, make that platinum!
